---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle={pageTitle}
  pageDescription={pageDescription}
  pageKeywords={pageKeywords}
>
  <div class="flex flex-col mx-auto mb-10 space-y-6 prose text-xl">
    <h1 class="mt-0 mb-4 text-4xl font-bold md:mb-6 md:text-5xl">Project Ideas</h1>
    <p>
      If you are a developer, you probably know this problem well: you have a million ideas for projects,
      but you do not have time to build all of them.
    </p>
    <p>
      So instead of letting them collect dust in Todoist, Obsidian, Google Keep, and random docs,
      I am writing them down here and sharing them publicly.
    </p>
    <p>
      These are sorted loosely by my current level of excitement, and that changes over time.
      Feel free to steal any of them.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have comments, questions, or want to build one together,
      <a href="mailto:kireevr1996@gmail.com">let me know</a>.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>Featured ideas</h2>
    {featuredIdeas.map((idea) => (
      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h3>{idea.title}</h3>
        <p>{idea.description}</p>
        {idea.notes.length > 0 && (
          <details>
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800">
              Additional notes
            </summary>
            <ul class="mt-2">
              {idea.notes.map((note) => (
                <li>{note}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </details>
        )}
      </section>
    ))}

    <hr />

    <h2>Google Keep backlog (new batch)</h2>
    <p>
      Raw ideas from Keep, lightly edited for clarity and deduplicated where possible.
      This list is intentionally broad: some are products, some are scripts, some are just experiments.
    </p>

    {keepIdeaGroups.map((group) => (
      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h3>{group.name}</h3>
        <ul>
          {group.ideas.map((idea) => (
            <li>
              <strong>{idea.title}:</strong> {idea.description}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>
    ))}
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
